.SH NAME
megasas_update_device_list \- Update the PD and LD device list from FW after an AEN event notification
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" megasas_update_device_list
.BI "(struct megasas_instance *instance "  ","
.BI "int event_type "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "instance" 12
Adapter soft state
.IP "event_type" 12
Indicates type of event (PD or LD event)
.SH "RETURN"
Success or failure
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Issue DCMDs to Firmware to update the internal device list in driver.
Based on the FW support, driver sends the HOST_DEVICE_LIST or combination
of PD_LIST/LD_LIST_QUERY DCMDs to get the device list.
